WEBVTT

01:31.380 --> 01:34.900
=Generation to Generation=

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
=Episode 27=

02:28.660 --> 02:29.500
For two hundred years,

02:30.010 --> 02:31.890
the Demon Sect has plagued the martial world.

02:32.610 --> 02:34.340
Thanks to our forebears of Beichen,

02:34.940 --> 02:35.820
who upheld justice and

02:36.260 --> 02:37.340
defended the righteous path,

02:38.060 --> 02:39.290
peace has endured

02:39.610 --> 02:40.980
despite countless perils.

02:41.940 --> 02:44.500
With the blessing of the Three Pure Ones

02:44.940 --> 02:46.380
and the spirits of our ancestors,

02:46.940 --> 02:48.170
we, unworthy disciples,

02:48.690 --> 02:49.730
have captured

02:50.060 --> 02:51.540
the Demon Sect's leader,

02:52.220 --> 02:53.130
Mu Qingyan.

02:54.130 --> 02:56.570
It is hereby decided that his meridians
be destroyed.

02:57.290 --> 02:58.130
Mu Qingyan,

02:59.500 --> 03:00.340
from now on,

03:00.610 --> 03:01.850
you may remain at Qingque Sect

03:02.290 --> 03:04.130
to cultivate and recuperate.

03:04.940 --> 03:05.780
No way.

03:06.170 --> 03:07.610
Then what do you want?

03:11.610 --> 03:12.660
Remove these shackles

03:13.890 --> 03:14.730
and let me go.

03:15.380 --> 03:16.220
Mu Qingyan,

03:17.410 --> 03:18.610
kneel when you speak!

03:19.890 --> 03:21.260
His injuries are too severe.

03:22.060 --> 03:22.900
He cannot kneel.

03:26.290 --> 03:27.540
Then make him crawl.

03:38.340 --> 03:40.100
Lord Yang, as a sect leader,

03:40.100 --> 03:41.290
have you no decorum?

03:41.290 --> 03:43.570
You expect decorum when dealing with a demon?

03:43.570 --> 03:44.420
Yuzhi.

03:44.430 --> 03:45.300
Enough.

03:45.780 --> 03:47.200
Everyone, calm down.

03:47.820 --> 03:49.890
Let Lord Qi preside.

03:50.780 --> 03:52.820
Others need not interrupt.

04:01.500 --> 04:02.340
Mu Qingyan,

04:02.980 --> 04:04.500
for the matter of Lord Wang alone,

04:05.260 --> 04:06.850
you could be executed.

04:07.610 --> 04:08.450
Now,

04:08.690 --> 04:10.220
we spare your life and merely

04:10.570 --> 04:11.730
destroy your meridians,

04:11.730 --> 04:13.570
this is Beichen's mercy.

04:33.810 --> 04:35.100
Standing by while others die,

04:37.220 --> 04:38.410
abetting evil,

04:39.170 --> 04:40.700
exterminating entire clans,

04:41.410 --> 04:42.850
is that

04:42.850 --> 04:43.930
your mercy?

04:44.340 --> 04:45.180
Mu Qingyan!

04:46.370 --> 04:48.100
You killed Lord Wang and now

04:48.900 --> 04:50.170
dare slander his name!

04:50.730 --> 04:51.610
That's not true!

04:53.290 --> 04:54.140
Zhao,

04:54.140 --> 04:55.050
the decision is made.

04:55.050 --> 04:55.890
Do not interfere.

04:56.410 --> 04:57.250
Zhao,

04:57.580 --> 04:59.250
he is the Demon Sect's leader.

04:59.930 --> 05:01.290
If we do not cripple him today,

05:01.660 --> 05:03.410
once he regains strength

05:03.780 --> 05:06.370
he will be a grave threat to the Six Sects.

05:07.980 --> 05:08.820
Carry out the sentence.

05:55.850 --> 05:56.690
Wait.

05:57.580 --> 05:58.420
Master,

05:58.560 --> 05:59.420
does there

05:59.420 --> 06:00.850
truly remain no other path?

06:01.290 --> 06:02.170
This is

06:02.170 --> 06:04.140
the only way to spare his life.

06:05.250 --> 06:06.090
Proceed.

06:45.900 --> 06:46.740
Master,

06:47.170 --> 06:48.490
if you cripple him today,

06:49.810 --> 06:51.220
I will not live.

06:53.250 --> 06:54.250
- Zhao!
- Zhao!

06:54.250 --> 06:55.090
Zhao!

07:02.490 --> 07:03.410
Zhao!

07:04.550 --> 07:05.400
Zhao!

07:05.490 --> 07:06.330
Zhao!

07:10.250 --> 07:11.100
Father!

07:13.990 --> 07:14.850
Master!

07:14.850 --> 07:15.690
Father!

07:21.370 --> 07:22.410
Cai Zhao!

07:53.050 --> 07:54.580
You unfilial disgrace!

08:11.290 --> 08:12.130
Zhao!

08:14.260 --> 08:15.130
Xiaofeng!

08:15.250 --> 08:16.090
Pingchun.

08:29.250 --> 08:30.090
How could she...

08:30.540 --> 08:31.660
It's Drizzle Numbing Powder.

08:33.850 --> 08:34.690
The tea?

08:35.370 --> 08:36.210
Yes.

08:37.100 --> 08:38.060
Foolish child.

09:06.420 --> 09:07.420
Zhao.

09:07.420 --> 09:08.850
Don't make another mistake.

09:08.850 --> 09:10.130
You can still turn back.

09:10.730 --> 09:11.850
There is no turning back.

09:13.980 --> 09:14.820
Zhao.

09:29.300 --> 09:30.340
Dad, what are you doing?

09:30.340 --> 09:31.730
Do you still want to marry Zhao?

09:31.730 --> 09:33.010
Then listen to me.

09:35.130 --> 09:36.420
If Mu escapes, so be it.

09:36.420 --> 09:38.090
We must do nothing now.

09:38.090 --> 09:38.930
Come on.

09:38.940 --> 09:40.840
Pretend the Chaos Needles are acting up

09:40.840 --> 09:41.700
and you can't move.

09:41.700 --> 09:42.540
Come on!

09:51.820 --> 09:53.420
Son, listen to me.

09:53.890 --> 09:55.850
If you go out now, will you help her save him

09:55.850 --> 09:56.820
or stop her?

09:56.820 --> 09:58.700
You must calm down.

09:58.700 --> 09:59.540
Stay.

10:13.490 --> 10:14.490
MoonLake?

10:16.370 --> 10:17.210
Let's break off the engagement.

10:18.420 --> 10:19.730
- Aunt once said,
- Pingshu.

10:19.730 --> 10:21.300
loving someone is not wrong,

10:22.010 --> 10:23.700
but if they don't love you the same way,

10:24.850 --> 10:26.220
don't hold on too long.

10:40.340 --> 10:41.180
I'm sorry.

10:41.730 --> 10:42.650
Uncle Zhou.

10:54.340 --> 10:55.610
Don't think you can escape!

10:55.610 --> 10:58.180
Even if he flees, he won't survive.

11:19.420 --> 11:20.260
My son!

11:24.250 --> 11:25.090
Zhao!

11:37.490 --> 11:38.330
Release the arrows!

11:38.650 --> 11:39.730
- No, stop!
- Stop!

11:39.730 --> 11:40.570
Cai Zhao!

11:41.130 --> 11:41.970
Stop!

11:44.890 --> 11:45.890
- Stop!
- Don't do it!

11:45.890 --> 11:47.130
- Stop!
- Stop!

11:47.130 --> 11:47.970
Stop!

11:49.940 --> 11:51.420
I'm sorry.

11:58.530 --> 12:00.060
Xiaofeng. Xiaofeng.

12:00.180 --> 12:01.020
Xiaofeng!

12:02.010 --> 12:02.940
Zhao,

12:02.940 --> 12:04.850
you heartless girl!

12:04.850 --> 12:07.060
If you wanted to free him, fine...

12:07.060 --> 12:08.530
but why leave as well?

12:14.130 --> 12:14.970
Chief,

12:21.580 --> 12:22.650
Cai Zhao

12:22.650 --> 12:23.700
colluded with the Demon Sect,

12:23.700 --> 12:24.940
betrayed her master and ancestors, and

12:24.940 --> 12:25.940
gravely injured fellow disciples.

12:25.940 --> 12:27.130
Her crimes are unforgivable.

12:27.130 --> 12:28.180
Issue a pursuit order

12:28.180 --> 12:29.420
to the world at once.

12:29.420 --> 12:30.890
Let all righteous sects

12:30.890 --> 12:32.180
hunt down and capture

12:33.100 --> 12:34.730
Mu Qingyan

12:34.730 --> 12:36.180
and the traitor

12:36.980 --> 12:37.820
Cai Zhao.

14:04.850 --> 14:05.690
Bear with it.

14:12.690 --> 14:14.420
♪In days gone by♪

14:14.730 --> 14:16.280
♪Willows swayed gently♪

14:16.580 --> 14:19.330
♪I first saw you in the dimness♪

14:20.300 --> 14:21.490
♪Amid the vast crowd♪

14:21.500 --> 14:22.970
♪A fleeting glance♪

14:23.140 --> 14:24.050
♪And then♪

14:24.060 --> 14:27.010
♪Love consumed me♪

14:27.820 --> 14:29.370
♪Now I think of you♪

14:29.770 --> 14:31.410
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

14:31.670 --> 14:33.010
♪Alas, we parted♪

14:33.020 --> 14:35.210
♪Longing for your return♪

14:35.340 --> 14:36.290
♪Moon waxes and wanes♪

14:36.300 --> 14:37.770
♪Letters can't convey my thoughts♪

14:37.780 --> 14:38.810
♪Scattered petals♪

14:38.820 --> 14:41.050
♪Cover the ground♪

14:43.150 --> 14:44.010
Zhao,

14:44.130 --> 14:44.970
are you all right?

14:46.010 --> 14:47.100
Let me apply some medicine.

14:49.250 --> 14:51.970
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

14:52.230 --> 14:56.170
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

14:56.890 --> 14:59.420
♪Such should be our meeting♪

14:59.700 --> 15:03.950
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

15:04.250 --> 15:06.830
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

15:07.210 --> 15:11.550
♪Tears are like pearls♪

15:27.730 --> 15:29.340
♪Now I think of you♪

15:29.670 --> 15:31.470
♪Snow and rain fall thickly♪

15:31.650 --> 15:32.890
♪Alas, we parted♪

15:32.890 --> 15:35.350
♪Longing for your return♪

15:35.350 --> 15:37.710
♪Moon waxes and wanes, letters can't convey
my thoughts♪

15:37.710 --> 15:38.620
♪Scattered petals♪

15:38.620 --> 15:41.420
♪Cover the ground♪

15:42.370 --> 15:45.710
♪Wedding candles glow, by the window we share♪

15:45.710 --> 15:48.150
♪Do you still remember♪

15:49.850 --> 15:52.220
♪A single light skiff drifting away?♪

15:52.220 --> 15:56.910
♪Where my brush falls, it's you♪

15:57.350 --> 15:59.190
♪Distant hills so clear♪

15:59.700 --> 16:04.370
♪Looking back, all worldly vanities disappear♪

16:06.280 --> 16:08.970
♪Such should be our meeting♪

16:08.970 --> 16:13.750
♪Golden wind brushes the jade dew♪

16:13.750 --> 16:16.230
♪Half shy, half joyful♪

16:16.560 --> 16:21.040
♪Wanting to leave yet lingering♪

16:21.210 --> 16:24.110
♪Such should be our meeting♪

16:24.110 --> 16:28.630
♪Across the Magpie Bridge♪

16:28.760 --> 16:31.250
♪Alas, peach blossoms have fallen♪

16:31.590 --> 16:36.700
♪Tears are like pearls♪

16:39.960 --> 16:42.430
♪Falling blossoms so fair♪

16:42.730 --> 16:44.900
♪Endless love beyond compare♪

16:44.980 --> 16:45.820
Mu Qingyan.

16:47.100 --> 16:47.940
Mu Qingyan,

16:48.490 --> 16:49.730
why are your injuries worsening?

16:51.850 --> 16:52.820
The needles...

16:53.700 --> 16:55.130
It's the execution needles.

17:00.980 --> 17:01.850
Mu Qingyan.

17:16.730 --> 17:18.090
(I've already infused him
with internal energy,)

17:18.530 --> 17:20.220
(why is he still alternating between chills
and heat?)

17:29.770 --> 17:32.900
Even if he flees, he won't survive.

17:39.220 --> 17:40.490
This poison is no weaker

17:40.490 --> 17:42.860
than Taichu Temple's Cold Spirit Powder.

17:43.490 --> 17:44.330
What is the Cold Spirit Powder?

17:44.730 --> 17:46.330
Taichu Temple's secret poison.

17:47.090 --> 17:49.980
They say it traps you between searing heat
and frozen agony.

17:50.490 --> 17:52.010
Ten days, and you're dead.

17:53.050 --> 17:53.890
But

17:53.890 --> 17:55.290
I already made an antidote.

17:55.770 --> 17:57.770
Snow lotus from the extreme coldness

17:58.220 --> 17:59.420
can cure it.

18:32.330 --> 18:33.290
The Lord's wounds

18:34.140 --> 18:35.220
look grave,

18:35.530 --> 18:36.530
but they're not life-threatening.

18:37.180 --> 18:38.570
Zhao held back.

18:38.980 --> 18:40.050
Held back?

18:40.810 --> 18:42.010
She schemed against the Lord,

18:42.330 --> 18:43.420
crippled Lord Zhou,

18:43.700 --> 18:44.570
injured her fellow disciples.

18:44.900 --> 18:46.180
That's outright treachery.

18:47.010 --> 18:47.940
Poor Ning

18:48.810 --> 18:49.940
fainted who knows how many times.

18:51.380 --> 18:52.420
I'll go check on Zhou.

19:12.220 --> 19:13.180
I never thought

19:15.090 --> 19:15.930
Zhao

19:17.490 --> 19:19.050
would follow Pingshu's path.

19:20.090 --> 19:21.380
Li Min coated the silver needles

19:21.900 --> 19:22.770
with Cold Spirit Powder.

19:23.660 --> 19:24.940
Mu Qingyan is as good as dead.

19:34.630 --> 19:35.540
Look.

19:35.540 --> 19:36.880
- How terrifying.
- Look at her.

20:08.380 --> 20:11.010
(He is in fine silks, but has
callused fingertips.)

20:11.420 --> 20:12.530
(He is an abacus man.)

20:13.290 --> 20:15.180
(A hard-working man should not be robbed.)

20:21.620 --> 20:23.290
(This one lives in luxury,)

20:23.290 --> 20:24.980
(yet treats her maid well.)

20:25.900 --> 20:29.700
(Not evil, I can't rob her either.)

20:58.180 --> 20:59.940
Luoying Valley

20:59.940 --> 21:02.140
truly breeds demonesses.

21:03.010 --> 21:04.860
Cai Zhao betrayed her master and sect,

21:04.860 --> 21:05.940
shameless.

21:05.940 --> 21:06.900
If I see her,

21:06.900 --> 21:08.530
I'll avenge Beichen's disciples.

21:09.490 --> 21:10.810
Lord Cai and his wife are pitiful.

21:11.660 --> 21:14.180
Her parents failed to raise her,
that's their karma.

21:14.770 --> 21:16.220
But Lord Qi

21:16.220 --> 21:18.980
trusted her for her mother's sake,

21:18.980 --> 21:20.180
even vouched for her.

21:21.140 --> 21:22.250
Trust misplaced.

22:07.490 --> 22:09.050
You must drink it.

22:30.570 --> 22:31.660
When you recover,

22:32.490 --> 22:34.090
I'll make you smiley

22:34.810 --> 22:36.620
so the medicine won't taste bitter.

22:48.090 --> 22:48.930
Did you know?

22:50.380 --> 22:53.290
In Luoying Valley, besides peach blossoms

22:53.940 --> 22:54.810
and wontons,

22:55.770 --> 22:56.700
our porridge

22:57.490 --> 22:58.490
is famous too.

22:59.860 --> 23:03.010
A couple runs the shop at the alley entrance,

23:04.980 --> 23:08.140
their chicken chestnut porridge is soft

23:08.530 --> 23:09.620
and fragrant.

23:15.050 --> 23:16.320
When I was five,

23:17.290 --> 23:18.250
my aunt was seriously ill.

23:19.050 --> 23:20.010
I sneaked out

23:20.420 --> 23:22.490
with a jar to buy her porridge.

23:24.730 --> 23:26.940
The shopkeeper was kind,

23:28.490 --> 23:30.180
though I had no money,

23:31.010 --> 23:33.570
she filled it anyway.

23:43.380 --> 23:45.490
But I was too small;

23:49.010 --> 23:51.660
the jar grew heavier with every step.

23:53.940 --> 23:55.090
The alley

23:57.090 --> 23:58.980
felt endless.

24:01.010 --> 24:02.730
I was exhausted.

24:03.700 --> 24:05.490
Just as I reached home,

24:07.490 --> 24:08.770
I tripped.

24:10.810 --> 24:12.220
The jar shattered.

24:13.900 --> 24:15.330
The porridge spilled everywhere.

24:31.980 --> 24:32.820
Mu Qingyan,

24:34.770 --> 24:35.860
for you,

24:37.700 --> 24:39.050
I hurt my master,

24:41.330 --> 24:42.810
my parents,

24:46.420 --> 24:47.940
and Uncle Zhou.

24:48.530 --> 24:50.090
I did all that.

24:51.620 --> 24:52.620
If you die,

24:53.490 --> 24:54.570
what does that make me?

24:56.770 --> 24:58.490
When my parents sent me to the sect,

24:59.180 --> 25:00.570
they warned me again and again...

25:01.570 --> 25:03.330
be obedient, never

25:04.090 --> 25:05.940
become a demoness.

25:10.770 --> 25:12.220
Yet here I am.

25:14.810 --> 25:16.010
Here I am.

25:22.700 --> 25:24.090
I miss home.

25:26.140 --> 25:27.140
In a few months,

25:28.010 --> 25:30.180
the tri-colored peach blossoms will bloom.

25:38.250 --> 25:40.090
Our valley has flowers all year...

25:41.010 --> 25:42.860
spring peaches,

25:42.860 --> 25:44.250
summer lotuses,

25:44.980 --> 25:46.380
autumn chrysanthemums,

25:47.140 --> 25:48.330
winter plums.

25:49.420 --> 25:50.490
One day,

25:55.570 --> 25:57.420
I want to show you all of it.

26:02.730 --> 26:03.570
Mu Qingyan,

26:09.180 --> 26:10.290
for me,

26:14.010 --> 26:15.490
you must live.

26:32.620 --> 26:33.700
How is it, Fengchi?

26:33.700 --> 26:34.660
Any news of Zhao?

26:35.090 --> 26:36.610
Someone who betrays her sect

26:36.900 --> 26:38.250
shouldn't return.

26:39.050 --> 26:41.250
It's not that severe.

26:41.250 --> 26:43.770
Master and Uncle Li weren't badly hurt.

26:43.770 --> 26:45.330
What about their hearts?

26:45.940 --> 26:46.940
Father adored Cai Zhao.

26:46.940 --> 26:48.810
Yet she plotted against her own.

26:48.810 --> 26:50.010
How heartbroken he must be?

26:50.770 --> 26:52.050
I even tried to help her.

26:52.980 --> 26:53.820
By the way,

26:54.180 --> 26:56.180
where did she get the Chaos Needles
and gunpowder?

26:57.010 --> 26:58.660
Weren't they locked in the armory?

27:00.090 --> 27:00.930
Zhao,

27:01.250 --> 27:02.380
I brought everything useful

27:02.380 --> 27:03.420
from the armory.

27:11.810 --> 27:12.650
Well,

27:12.860 --> 27:13.940
Uncle Lei asked me to deliver medicine.

27:14.180 --> 27:15.020
I have to go.

27:15.490 --> 27:16.380
Did I do wrong?

27:16.380 --> 27:17.220
Xingjia.

27:18.010 --> 27:19.940
God of Wealth, Guanyin,

27:19.940 --> 27:21.860
please keep her safe.

27:22.220 --> 27:23.810
Please, please.

27:28.730 --> 27:29.900
This is Zhao's?

27:33.220 --> 27:34.140
Let me see.

27:37.290 --> 27:39.220
The town connects in all directions,

27:39.220 --> 27:40.180
and there was no witness.

27:41.140 --> 27:42.620
There are no trace

27:42.620 --> 27:44.250
of Mu Qingyan or Cai Zhao.

27:45.180 --> 27:46.860
The Six Sects and Nie Zhe are hunting them.

27:47.510 --> 27:49.500
Hiding deep in the mountains would be safer.

27:50.220 --> 27:51.490
Why risk a town?

27:51.940 --> 27:53.280
She went to a clinic,

27:53.730 --> 27:54.570
bought snow lotus.

27:54.900 --> 27:55.740
Snow lotus?

27:56.570 --> 27:58.660
Isn't that for detoxifying?

27:59.220 --> 28:00.570
Mu Qingyan is injured.

28:01.660 --> 28:02.700
They can't go far.

28:03.220 --> 28:04.420
I've sent carrier pigeons

28:05.140 --> 28:07.090
to every sect and wandering knight.

28:07.570 --> 28:09.620
Soon we'll have

28:09.620 --> 28:10.900
their trail.

28:12.050 --> 28:12.980
Master,

28:12.980 --> 28:14.020
let me go myself.

28:18.460 --> 28:22.020
(Past and Future Glory)

28:22.050 --> 28:22.890
Yuzhi.

28:23.160 --> 28:24.020
Yuzhi.

28:24.140 --> 28:24.980
Wait for me.

28:29.380 --> 28:30.420
Don't blame me

28:30.420 --> 28:31.490
for stopping you earlier.

28:31.940 --> 28:34.250
Who knew that girl would strike so ruthlessly?

28:35.490 --> 28:37.220
Now we take it step by step.

28:37.220 --> 28:38.090
She's sentimental.

28:39.250 --> 28:40.290
She owes Mu Qingyan

28:40.730 --> 28:42.380
so she won't let him die.

28:43.010 --> 28:44.010
Once he heals,

28:44.010 --> 28:45.570
she'll return.

28:45.570 --> 28:46.940
If you were so certain,

28:46.940 --> 28:48.810
you wouldn't volunteer to chase her.

28:48.810 --> 28:51.330
She acts without rules,

28:51.330 --> 28:52.220
and that Mu boy

28:52.220 --> 28:53.900
is as handsome as you.

28:53.900 --> 28:55.420
She might never

28:55.420 --> 28:56.730
come back.

28:57.700 --> 29:00.290
Don't listen to your mother.

29:00.290 --> 29:02.420
Life is short,

29:02.420 --> 29:03.860
you should just

29:03.860 --> 29:05.140
do as you please.

29:07.490 --> 29:08.330
Win her back if you must.

29:09.490 --> 29:10.530
There's nothing shameful.

29:18.050 --> 29:19.290
Good boy.

29:30.420 --> 29:31.260
Zhao.

29:32.700 --> 29:33.540
You're awake.

29:50.810 --> 29:52.090
The poison's stable now.

29:53.050 --> 29:53.890
I thought

29:55.050 --> 29:55.980
you'd gone home.

29:56.380 --> 29:57.290
How could I

29:58.180 --> 29:59.050
leave you like this?

30:00.220 --> 30:01.530
Taste the porridge later.

30:01.530 --> 30:02.410
My aunt said

30:02.410 --> 30:03.490
I was as good as the shop.

30:06.980 --> 30:08.010
I heard everything,

30:10.490 --> 30:11.530
about Luoying Valley.

30:13.620 --> 30:15.810
Was I foolish as a child?

30:18.290 --> 30:20.010
I like your childhood stories.

30:21.010 --> 30:22.500
Your home sounds

30:23.730 --> 30:25.090
whole and bright,

30:25.860 --> 30:27.220
just thinking of it brings joy.

30:29.860 --> 30:30.860
Unlike mine.

30:31.530 --> 30:32.700
If you like,

30:33.730 --> 30:35.050
I'll share half of my childhood with you.

30:35.660 --> 30:36.980
Then when you remember it,

30:37.490 --> 30:38.980
you'll feel joy too.

30:48.050 --> 30:48.890
Careful.

30:49.180 --> 30:51.050
Li Min poisoned the needles.

30:51.770 --> 30:52.900
He meant to kill me.

30:53.490 --> 30:54.770
Whoever applied the poison,

30:56.140 --> 30:57.700
the executioner must know.

30:58.330 --> 30:59.860
Uncle Li?

31:00.620 --> 31:02.220
He's always been fair.

31:02.700 --> 31:03.620
He and Master...

31:46.220 --> 31:47.060
Zhao.

31:48.980 --> 31:49.820
Let's

31:52.490 --> 31:53.900
rely on each other from now on.

31:57.290 --> 31:58.660
Let's find somewhere quiet

31:59.330 --> 32:00.180
and leave the martial world.

32:02.140 --> 32:02.980
Okay?

32:48.770 --> 32:49.940
(Zhao.)

32:58.250 --> 32:59.250
It's been so long,

33:00.330 --> 33:02.140
Mu Qingyan still hasn't been found.

33:02.810 --> 33:04.940
Shangguan and You Guanyue

33:05.420 --> 33:06.570
may not be trying hard.

33:07.420 --> 33:08.730
They surrendered

33:09.220 --> 33:11.050
only because they thought

33:11.530 --> 33:12.770
Mu Qingyan would die after capture.

33:13.660 --> 33:14.500
Who knew

33:14.660 --> 33:16.180
the Six Sects

33:16.620 --> 33:17.860
would lose him

33:18.180 --> 33:19.220
at the execution ground?

33:19.810 --> 33:21.420
If he lives,

33:21.980 --> 33:22.940
I'm afraid

33:24.090 --> 33:26.220
those two will waver.

33:26.980 --> 33:27.820
Elder Hu,

33:28.010 --> 33:29.620
go deal with it.

33:30.730 --> 33:31.940
If they're still colluding

33:31.940 --> 33:33.490
with Mu Qingyan,

33:34.730 --> 33:36.250
eliminate them.

33:36.250 --> 33:37.090
Yes.

33:53.570 --> 33:55.050
The Hanhai Mountains are ahead.

33:55.940 --> 33:57.140
Rest tonight.

34:07.250 --> 34:08.420
Miss Cai,

34:08.420 --> 34:09.340
clever as you are,

34:10.490 --> 34:11.330
you must know

34:12.420 --> 34:13.530
I fear not just the dark,

34:14.170 --> 34:15.260
but sleeping alone.

34:48.130 --> 34:48.980
So beautiful.

35:05.090 --> 35:07.090
A foreign moon can't

35:08.300 --> 35:10.300
outshine the lamp of home.

35:11.170 --> 35:13.610
I know you miss home.

35:49.130 --> 35:49.970
You miss

35:52.610 --> 35:53.900
your valley,

35:55.940 --> 35:57.010
your parents,

35:59.570 --> 36:00.420
your brother.

36:21.980 --> 36:22.820
Zhao,

36:25.340 --> 36:26.180
trust me.

36:30.490 --> 36:31.530
You will go back.

37:16.841 --> 37:27.501
=Generation to Generation=

37:46.261 --> 37:50.671
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

37:51.236 --> 37:55.851
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

37:56.191 --> 38:00.756
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

38:01.281 --> 38:05.581
♪Free to wander in the world♪

38:08.526 --> 38:13.226
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:13.751 --> 38:18.041
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

38:18.701 --> 38:22.731
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

38:23.046 --> 38:28.171
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

38:28.746 --> 38:33.556
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

38:33.771 --> 38:37.941
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

38:38.666 --> 38:42.601
♪I freely roam in the world♪

38:43.101 --> 38:48.376
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

39:11.106 --> 39:16.236
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

39:16.601 --> 39:20.971
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

39:21.236 --> 39:25.366
♪I freely roam in the world♪

39:25.551 --> 39:31.126
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪
